  "title": "Student Care Teacher (Part-Time)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>Plan and implement curriculum for the students</p></li><li><p>Supervision of schoolwork for the students</p></li><li><p>Preferably able to teach upper primary students all subjects(English/Chinese/Maths/Science)</p></li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Able to commit to working up to 32 hours per week: Mon to Thurs: 12.30pm to 7.00pm; Fri: 1.00pm to 7.00pm</li><li>Applicants must be willing to work in Woodlands/Admiralty</li><li>Relevant working experience in education or student care setting is preferred</li><li>Passionate and patient in helping children</li><li>Ability to work independently with minimal supervision</li><li>A strong team player and receptive to changes</li></ul><p><u><strong>Qualifications</strong></u>:</p><ul><li>GCE 5 \"O\" Level / Pre-U / A level / Diploma in any field</li><li>Should be proficient in Mandarin language to teach Mandarin as a subject to the students</li><li>Should be able to commit to a permanent part-time arrangement for minimum one year to avoid any disruption to the student's learning schedule.</li></ul><p><strong>Please apply for this position via this link </strong><a href=\"https://carecorner.wd102.myworkdayjobs.com/en-US/CCS/job/Care-Staff_JR-00129\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a><a href=\"https://carecorner.wd102.myworkdayjobs.com/CCS/job/Singapore/Student-Care-Teacher--Part-Time-_JR-00140\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Careers</a><strong>.</strong><br /><br /><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified for interviews.</p>",
